&lt;p&gt;We’re a venture-backed company that has raised over $35M to date and is supported by experienced investors and long-term partners. We’re a growth-focused business building for scale, and we’re excited by the opportunities and challenges that come with that journey.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;LearnLux is looking for a full time dual Certified Financial Planner® and licensed Tax Specialist to join our fast growing team. Leveraging the LearnLux digital experience you will work directly with employees to provide them with unbiased, holistic financial and tax guidance. Your extensive financial experience and client-first approach will help employees prepare for and accomplish their personal and financial goals.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is 100% remote within the US and reports to the Director of Financial Planning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Our planners provide coverage at various shifts from 7 AM - 11 PM ET Monday through Fridays and 9 AM - 4PM ET on Saturdays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Meet and engage with clients remotely over video, chat and email to give guidance on topics like budgeting, student loans, retirement readiness, equity compensation, debt management, taxes and more&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advise on the LearnLux methodology to improve and respond to the changing financial environment&lt;/li&gt;
