&lt;li&gt;Work with our content team to create outlines, lessons, video content, review lessons and approve content created for the LearnLux digital platform&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and lead engagement campaigns for our employer partners like digital webinars and occasional on-site events&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
